# PORTFOLIO-REQ-03 - Portfolio Gated Advancement Review

Date: 2026-06-08

Workspace: `/opt/Axodus`

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This report is local/unversioned unless migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Summary

PORTFOLIO-REQ-03 consolidates the portfolio advancement decision after:

- Portfolio Status Normalization;
- Portfolio Validation Refresh;
- TRADING-REQ-04 Safe Local Postgres E2E Revalidation;
- ACS-GATE-01 L4 Candidate Evidence Review.

No product features were implemented. No production integrations, secrets, wallet signing, treasury movement, swaps, minting, settlement, payouts, production credentials, contract deployment, trading execution or production readiness claims were introduced.

Portfolio recommendation: `PORTFOLIO_READY_FOR_SELECTIVE_L4_ADVANCEMENT`

Selected next cycle: `Business L4 Consolidation`

