## Blocker Severity

| Severity | Nuclei | Summary |
|---|---|---|
| HIGH | Marketplace, ACS, Lottery, Trading, Defi | Payment/settlement, autonomous execution, prize/payout, live trading, custody/treasury or compliance-sensitive blockers. |
| MEDIUM | Documentation, Dex, Business, Mining, Academy, BBA-Agency, AxodusAPP, Governance | Publication, provider, billing, rewards, schema, integration or transport blockers that do not prevent bounded planning/consolidation. |
| LOW | Core | Strong contractual evidence, but still pre-RC and non-runtime. |

## Portfolio Balance

The portfolio now has materially stronger maturity symmetry than before Portfolio Status Normalization:

- Core and Governance remain high-confidence L5 contractual nuclei.
- Documentation and Dex are L4 readiness tracks, not publication/execution tracks.
- Business, Mining, Academy, Marketplace, ACS and Trading now have L4 candidate evidence or gate-reviewed L4 candidate decisions.
- BBA-Agency and Lottery remain L3 local/mock candidates.
- Defi and AxodusAPP remain special-case readiness/planning/integration tracks.

The portfolio is ready for selective L4 advancement, but not for production release or execution-sensitive activation.

## Executive Recommendation

Recommendation: `PORTFOLIO_READY_FOR_SELECTIVE_L4_ADVANCEMENT`

Rationale:

- Business, Mining, Academy, Marketplace, ACS and Trading have current validation evidence.
- Trading and ACS had their remaining gate decisions completed after the validation refresh.
- Multiple nuclei can now support bounded L4 consolidation work.
- Production-sensitive blockers remain explicit and active.
- No nucleus is approved for production readiness.

## Selected Next Cycle

Selected next cycle: `Business L4 Consolidation`

Justification:

- Business has high evidence quality after `npm run check` passed with build, validators and 102 tests.
- Business is a central integration domain for enterprise/customer/runtime contracts.
- Business L4 consolidation can be scoped to repository contracts, persistence boundaries, billing policy documentation and non-executing integration readiness.
- It has lower immediate execution sensitivity than Marketplace settlement, Academy rewards/contracts, Mining payouts, ACS execution authority or Trading exchange execution.

